ActCanadian Navigable Waters Act
SubjectOrder Exempting Kapisikama Lake, Located in Quebec, from the Application of Section 23 of the Canadian Navigable Waters Act
PrecisORDER EXEMPTING KAPISIKAMA LAKE, LOCATED IN QUEBEC, FROM THE APPLICATION OF SECTION 23 OF THE CANADIAN NAVIGABLE WATERS ACT in order to permit dewatering to reduce water levels in Kapisikama Lake to facilitate mining operations.
